For us IBM means a long-term thought of continuous movements directed towards the future.
IBM has survived a hundred years because it remains faithful to its core values and yet has not been afraid to change all others around it.
This allowed us in our first century to transform technology, business and society.
We hope that in the second century we will reach even more," the current director of the company Samuel J. Palmisano announced for the anniversary.
