It has been working at IBM for thirty years and is currently serving as Head of Sales, Marketing and Strategy.
In recent years IBM has been doing what is called jamy, brain-storming online from what are derived from many future strategies and innovations.
It is not surprising that there are many ideas - in the firm there are nearly 500,000 people who work.
An institution with a good name
It is the internal and external image of the company that provides it with a secure position in the business field.
