This is an excerpt from the conversation, whose complete transcription is found in La Nación on the Internet.
For its Costa Rican followers, the fact that Pearl Jam will occur in Costa Rica is a dream come true. Are you aware of what your fans live?
Going to Costa Rica is a dream that has become a reality for us too.
This is our second time in South and Central America and has so far been great.
